Welcome to AgentPitstop.com
Welcome to AgentPitstop.com, the agent mobile resource for Van Berg & Associates agents and their affiliates. Van Berg & Associates has more than 17 years of experience in the Senior Market. We pride ourselves on providing our agents with competitive carriers and top notch service, as well as developing new technology and tools for our agents to assist in growing their books of business. We acknowledge that the Medicare market has frequent changes in regulations and rules affecting how we do business, and compliance has never been so important. Because of this, we make every effort to keep our agents and brokers informed of these changes so they can continue to run their business in compliance.


